    <title>测试</title>
    <url>/markdown-test.html</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="博客搭建"><a href="#博客搭建" class="headerlink" title="博客搭建"></a>博客搭建</h1><p>本博客通过<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/configuration.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hexo</a>搭建，采用<a href="https://github.com/theme-next/awesome-next#live-preview" target="_blank" rel="noopener">NexT</a>主题，博客内容用markdown编辑，再由hexo自动生成html文件，发布在本博客上。</p>
<h2 id="Markdown"><a href="#Markdown" class="headerlink" title="Markdown"></a>Markdown</h2><p><a href="https://www.runoob.com/markdown/md-tutorial.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Markdown</a>，文件扩展名通常为 “.md”，是一种语法非常简洁的标记语言，熟悉语法的人完全可以通过任何文本编辑器编辑，如txt文本编辑器Notepad，<a href="http://blog.csdn.net/liyuanbhu/article/details/51112353" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CSDN</a>中曾介绍过几款不错的编辑器，如<a href="http://www.open-open.com/lib/view/open1410054722826.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">smark</a>，<a href="http://pad.haroopress.com/user.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Haroopad</a>。</p>
<h2 id="数学公式"><a href="#数学公式" class="headerlink" title="数学公式"></a>数学公式</h2><p><a href="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/MATH.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">NexT支持MathJax和Katex渲染markdown文本中的数学公式</a>，本博客通过测试采用了MathJax引擎，通过kramed渲染器实现渲染。</p>
<h3 id="行内公式"><a href="#行内公式" class="headerlink" title="行内公式"></a>行内公式</h3><p>例如：$a=\sqrt{b}$</p>
<h3 id="行间公式"><a href="#行间公式" class="headerlink" title="行间公式"></a>行间公式</h3><p>例如：</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\frac{1}{n^{2}}</script><h3 id="方程组"><a href="#方程组" class="headerlink" title="方程组"></a>方程组</h3><p>例如<br><figure class="highlight tex"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="formula">$$</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="formula"><span class="tag">\<span class="name">begin</span><span class="string">&#123;align&#125;</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="formula"><span class="tag">\<span class="name">sqrt</span><span class="string">&#123;37&#125;</span></span> &amp; = <span class="tag">\<span class="name">sqrt</span><span class="string">&#123;\frac&#123;73^2-1&#125;</span><span class="string">&#123;12^2&#125;</span></span>&#125; <span class="tag">\<span class="name">nonumber</span></span> <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="formula"> &amp; = <span class="tag">\<span class="name">sqrt</span><span class="string">&#123;\frac&#123;73^2&#125;</span><span class="string">&#123;12^2&#125;</span></span><span class="tag">\<span class="name">cdot</span></span><span class="tag">\<span class="name">frac</span><span class="string">&#123;73^2-1&#125;</span><span class="string">&#123;73^2&#125;</span></span>&#125; <span class="tag">\<span class="name">nonumber</span></span> <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="formula"> &amp; = <span class="tag">\<span class="name">sqrt</span><span class="string">&#123;\frac&#123;73^2&#125;</span><span class="string">&#123;12^2&#125;</span></span>&#125;<span class="tag">\<span class="name">sqrt</span><span class="string">&#123;\frac&#123;73^2-1&#125;</span><span class="string">&#123;73^2&#125;</span></span>&#125; <span class="tag">\<span class="name">nonumber</span></span> <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="formula"> &amp; = <span class="tag">\<span class="name">frac</span><span class="string">&#123;73&#125;</span><span class="string">&#123;12&#125;</span></span><span class="tag">\<span class="name">sqrt</span><span class="string">&#123;1 - \frac&#123;1&#125;</span><span class="string">&#123;73^2&#125;</span></span>&#125; <span class="tag">\<span class="name">nonumber</span></span> <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="formula"> &amp; <span class="tag">\<span class="name">approx</span></span> <span class="tag">\<span class="name">frac</span><span class="string">&#123;73&#125;</span><span class="string">&#123;12&#125;</span></span><span class="tag">\<span class="name">left</span></span>(1 - <span class="tag">\<span class="name">frac</span><span class="string">&#123;1&#125;</span><span class="string">&#123;2\cdot73^2&#125;</span></span><span class="tag">\<span class="name">right</span></span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="formula"><span class="tag">\<span class="name">end</span><span class="string">&#123;align&#125;</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="formula">$$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>的执行结果为：</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">
\begin{align}
\sqrt{37} & = \sqrt{\frac{73^2-1}{12^2}} \nonumber \\
 & = \sqrt{\frac{73^2}{12^2}\cdot\frac{73^2-1}{73^2}} \nonumber \\
 & = \sqrt{\frac{73^2}{12^2}}\sqrt{\frac{73^2-1}{73^2}} \nonumber \\
 & = \frac{73}{12}\sqrt{1 - \frac{1}{73^2}} \nonumber \\
 & \approx \frac{73}{12}\left(1 - \frac{1}{2\cdot73^2}\right)
\end{align}</script><h2 id="图片"><a href="#图片" class="headerlink" title="图片"></a>图片</h2><p><img src="http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/2548020-3406fb0ee1867d77.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="blog.png"></p>
]]></content>
